"Joe Ma Tak-Chung (Chinese: 馬德鐘) is a Hong Kong actor. He was a policeman before he joined the Hong Kong entertainment industry in 1993. He is one of few Hong Kong actors who were former members of Hong Kong discipline or colonial services. Ma is most known for his extensive career with broadcaster TVB, particularly for the dramas \"Journey to the West\" (1996), \"Triumph in the Skies\" (2003), and \"The Drive of Life\" (2007).","name":"Joe Ma Tak-Chung","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"马德钟（Joe Ma，1968年6月27日－），祖籍广东潮州，生于香港，前香港警员，无线电视部头合约男艺员，于赵聿修纪念中学毕业，于1991年拍摄电视广告而入行，于1993年加入无线电视。入行前为皇家G4特警、排球运动员。主要代表作：《创世纪》、《冲上云霄》、《酒店风云》、《 凤凰四重奏》、《飞虎》。 1986年毕业于皇家 香港警察少年训练学校，1989年考入G4特警，1989年入选香港排球队，代表香港备战亚运。1991年在朋友介绍下做兼职模特入行。1993年因一则电视广告被香港无线电视(TVB)发掘进入演艺圈。2000年凭借《创世纪》崭露头角。2002年于《无考不成冤家》首次担任男主角。2003年凭借《冲上云霄》成功上位成为当红一线小生。","name":"马德钟","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"馬德鍾","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"馬德鐘（Joe Ma，1968 年 6 月 27 日－），祖籍廣東潮州，生於香港，前香港警員，無線電視部頭合約男藝員，於趙聿修紀念中學畢業，於 1991 年拍攝電視廣告而入行，於 1993 年加入無線電視。入行前為皇家 G4 特警、排球運動員。主要代表作：《創世紀》、《衝上雲霄》、《酒店風雲》、《 鳳凰四重奏》、《飛虎》。\n\n1986 年畢業於皇家 香港警察少年訓練學校，1989 年考入 G4 特警，1989 年入選香港排球隊，代表香港備戰亞運。1991 年在朋友介紹下做兼職模特入行。1993 年因一則電視廣告被香港無線電視 (TVB) 發掘進入演藝圈。2000 年憑藉《創世紀》嶄露頭角。2002 年於《無考不成冤家》首次擔任男主角。2003 年憑藉《衝上雲霄》成功上位成為當紅一線小生。","name":"馬德鐘","primary":true}}]}},"person_552022_translations":{"at":1772691649235,"data":{"id":552022,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SE","iso_639_1":"sv","name":"svenska","english_name":"Swedish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Figge Norling","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Figge Norling","primary":false}}]}},"person_1380129_translations":{"at":1772691650876,"data":{"id":1380129,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Deanna Allison","primary":true}}]}},"person_1223071_translations":{"at":1772691657871,"data":{"id":1223071,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"郭羡妮（Sonija Kwok），1974年7月22日出生于中国香港，拥有四分之一的英国血统。毕业于西蒙弗雷泽大学，女演员。\n\n1999年获得香港小姐冠军。2000年获得国际华裔小姐冠军后签约香港无线，从而进入演艺圈。2001年出演TVB古装穿越科幻剧《寻秦记》走红。2003年因主演古装剧《帝女花》和《牛郎织女》获得更多关注。2006年，郭羡妮凭借武侠剧《游剑江湖》中饰演的云紫萝一角获得金南方年度最受欢迎港台女艺人。2008年主演TVB时装剧《古灵精探B》和亚视古装神话剧《八仙过海》。2013年，主演民初喜剧《初五启市录》。2014年，出演古装神话剧《无双谱》。","name":"郭羡妮","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Sonija Kwok Sin-nei (Chinese: 郭羨妮, born 22 July 1974) is a Hongkonger actress, model and beauty pageant titleholder who worked with TVB from 1999 to 2015. Since 2015 she has been managed by GAIA Entertainment.","name":"Sonija Kwok Sin-Nae","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"郭羨妮，香港女演員，曾是無綫電視旗下藝人。她是中英混血兒，曾當過機艙服務員；其後參加選美，成為 1999 年度香港小姐冠軍及於美國拉斯維加斯舉辦的 2000 年度國際華裔小姐競選冠軍，歷史性成為 1990 年代最後一位香港小姐冠軍，及千禧年代首位國際華裔小姐冠軍；更是千禧年代首個國際選美比賽的冠軍，及第二位同時獲得香港小姐冠軍和國際華裔小姐冠軍的佳麗。參選時酷似 1991 年最上鏡小姐樊亦敏，故當時被傳媒稱為「翻版樊亦敏」。\n\n其後開始演出電視劇，首部參演便是重頭劇《尋秦記》，飾演兩大女主角之一的琴清。2002 年在電視劇《洛神》中飾演反派角色令觀眾形象深刻。2014 年 1 月，郭羨妮接拍無綫電視重頭劇《無雙譜》，與黎耀祥、田蕊妮、黃浩然、黃宗澤、龔嘉欣、岑麗香等人合作。2015 年 8 月，她和同屆港姐季軍胡杏兒因約滿而離開無線，兩人結束 16 年之賓主關係，《無雙譜》是她在無綫的告別作。2019 年，香港電影《朝花夕拾．芳華絕代 — 拾芳》於「第七屆温哥華華語電影節 (7th Vancouver Chinese Film Festival)」獲得四大獎項，當中包括年度最佳粵語片、高志森與梁柏豪獲「最佳導演獎」、胡杏兒獲「最佳女主角獎」，而她獲得「新鋭人氣獎」。","name":"郭羨妮","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Quách Thiện Ni","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"郭羨妮","primary":false}}]}},"person_1957064_translations":{"at":1772691659168,"data":{"id":1957064,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"NL","iso_639_1":"nl","name":"Nederlands","english_name":"Dutch","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Chris Collins is a former US Marine based in Hong Kong. He runs a martial arts school in Hong Kong and has affiliates worldwide. He is an actor and action director under SUN Entertainment. His tutelage in the industry is from Sammo Hung, Nicky Li and Donnie Yen.","name":"Chris Collins","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"克里斯·柯林斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"克里斯·柯林斯","primary":false}}]}},"movie_1327688_credits":{"at":1772691666574,"data":{"id":1327688,"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":11864,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Ryan Phillippe","original_name":"Ryan Phillippe","popularity":3.7075,"profile_path":"/lDqc0Tl5PrXbXYBxhA11MRLlbfG.jpg","cast_id":1,"character":"Danny","credit_id":"66b66515190bf3d7f52707ed","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":2333351,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Amélie Hoeferle","original_name":"Amélie Hoeferle","popularity":6.2548,"profile_path":"/7As5CmmphS4xXVkoIkVApFlxzXV.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"Alex","credit_id":"66b6652227c98b0e0bc4e62d","order":1},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":221840,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Sara Canning","original_name":"Sara Canning","popularity":1.5143,"profile_path":"/55AL7y8ybTE7uvpQALughR7bkkB.jpg","cast_id":6,"character":"Janine","credit_id":"66ce66f57cef7757bba09282","o